[[File:Battlepoints.png|thumb|200px|A Battle Point]]
==Description== The currency earned from the [[Battle Frontier]].
==Multipliers==
There is a hidden multiplier called the Battle Multiplier that is determined by The last stage you've beaten divided by 100, but is at least 1. --> (StageBeaten / 100, 1) = battleMultiplier
===Rates=== {| class="wikitable" |- ! Awarded !! Rate |- | [[Battle Points]] || stageBeaten * battleMultiplier |- | Money || stageBeaten * 100 * battleMultiplier |}
==Uses== Used to buy items from the Battle Frontier Shop. ===Battle Frontier Shop=== {| class="wikitable" |- ! Items available !! Starting price !! Price Increment !! Max Price |- | [[Ultraball]] || 1 [[File:Battlepoints.png|15px]] || 0% Previous Price || 1 [[File:Battlepoints.png|15px]] |- | [[Masterball]] || 500 [[File:Battlepoints.png|15px]] || 135% Previous Price || 50000 [[File:Battlepoints.png|15px]] |- | [[Small Restore]] || 10 [[File:Battlepoints.png|15px]] || 0% Previous Price || 10 [[File:Battlepoints.png|15px]] |- | [[Medium Restore]] || 20 [[File:Battlepoints.png|15px]] || 0% Previous Price || 20 [[File:Battlepoints.png|15px]] |- | [[Large Restore]] || 40 [[File:Battlepoints.png|15px]] || 0% Previous Price || 40 [[File:Battlepoints.png|15px]] |}

